-- Snamprogetti Resolves Nigerian Bribery Case With U.S. Government Accord
-- David Voreacos
-- 2010-07-07T16:47:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-07/snamprogetti-resolves-nigerian-bribery-case-with-u-s-government-accord.html

          
          
             Snamprogetti SPA resolved a Nigerian
bribery case today in a deferred prosecution agreement with the
U.S. In an agreement filed in federal court in Houston the
company agreed to pay $240 million in criminal penalties.  
